 "title": "Warm chocolate pudding – From my days on the farm",
 "excerpt": "I made the pudding tonight for my dear family from Nelspruit who are coming to visit tomorrow. It's rich and delicious. My mother used to make it for us often on the farm. BATTER: 65 ml butter 65 ml milk 1 egg 190 ml sugar 250 ml flour 15 ml baking powder 60 …",
 "seo": {
  "title": "Warm chocolate pudding - From my days on the farm - Marinda Kook",
  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>I made the pudding tonight for my dear family from Nelspruit who are coming to visit tomorrow. It's rich and delicious. My mother used to make it for us often on the farm.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">BATTER:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>65 ml butter</li>\n<li>65 ml milk</li>\n<li>1 egg</li>\n<li>190 ml sugar</li>\n<li>250 ml flour</li>\n<li>15 ml baking powder</li>\n<li>60 ml cocoa</li>\n<li>2,5 ml salt</li>\n<li>5 ml vanilla essence<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-700\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 002\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-002-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">SAUCE:<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-012.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-704\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 012\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-012-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>750 ml boiling water</li>\n<li>750 ml sugar</li>\n<li>60 ml cocoa<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-016.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-705\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 016\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-016-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Stir all the sauce ingredients together until the sugar has dissolved.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">NOW: &#8211; for the batter</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>melt the butter and milk together</li>\n<li>whisk the egg and sugar together<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-701\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>add the dry ingredients and vanilla essence to the egg mixture<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-008.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-702\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 008\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-008-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>now mix in the butter/milk mixture<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-707\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 023\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-023-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>grease an ovenproof dish and pour the sauce into the bottom of the dish<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-706\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-018-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>spoon dollops of the batter onto the sauce<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-030.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-708\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 030\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-030-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>bake for 30 minutes at 180 degrees Celsius<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-084.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-712\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 084\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-084-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>sprinkle icing sugar over the pudding<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-085.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-711\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 085\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-085-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Eat this big treat with custard, ice cream or cream. You'll never look back and think chocolate is just for Easter eggs again. I made a double batch, because from experience I know it's never enough.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-114.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-709\" alt=\"sjok poeding, boud en doek vir blog 114\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/sjok-poeding-boud-en-doek-vir-blog-114-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
 "recipe": null
}
